        <type>reg</type>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <text>
            <![CDATA["I am a magical construct, created to deliver certain programmed messages, I was placed here by the mage Palhatis."]]>
        </text>
    </node>
    <node for="160">
        <keyword>prog</keyword>
        <keyword>mess</keyword>
        <type>reg</type>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <text>
            <![CDATA["The School was only given one week to close. For this reason, much virulently poisonous waste was left inside. Any leaks would result in incredible destruction. This upset Palhatis, so he took steps to prevent a disaster."]]>
        </text>
    </node>
    <node for="160">
        <keyword>mage</keyword>
        <keyword>palh</keyword>
        <type>reg</type>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <text>
            <![CDATA[It continues, in a completely emotionless voice. "The mage Palhatis was one of the administrators for the School of Magery. When the Empire closed the School, he was murdered."]]>
        </text>
    </node>
    <node for="160">
        <keyword>scho</keyword>
        <keyword>mage</keyword>
        <type>reg</type>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <text>
            <![CDATA["The School of Magery. Research and education facility. Closed by the Empire."]]>
        </text>
    </node>
    <node for="160">
        <keyword>murd</keyword>
        <keyword>xxxx</keyword>
        <type>reg</type>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <text>
            <![CDATA["Many here were killed by Vinnia, on orders from the Empire, when the school was closed. It was thought that they were disloyal.]]>
        </text>
    </node>
    <node for="160">
        <keyword>vinn</keyword>
        <keyword>disl</keyword>
        <type>reg</type>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <text>
            <![CDATA["Vinnia was an administrator, and very loyal to the Empire."]]>
        </text>
    </node>
    <node for="160">
        <keyword>clos</keyword>
        <keyword>empi</keyword>
        <type>reg</type>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <text>
            <![CDATA["The leaders of the Empire decided that magical power could only be trusted when centralized under their direct control. The research of the School of Magery was so successful that it was the first to be closed."]]>
        </text>
        <text>
            <![CDATA["The haste of its closure was the reason for my message."]]>
        </text>
    </node>
    <node for="160">
        <keyword>rese</keyword>
        <keyword>xxxx</keyword>
        <type>reg</type>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <text>
            <![CDATA["Magical thinking devices. This is irrelevant to my message."]]>
        </text>
    </node>
    <node for="160">
        <keyword>step</keyword>
        <keyword>disa</keyword>
        <type>reg</type>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <text>
            <![CDATA["Although all of the controls and devices in the School were to be deactivated, he made sure that the controls to the waste disposal unit remained. These controls might still be activated."]]>
        </text>
    </node>
    <node for="160">
        <keyword>cont</keyword>
        <keyword>acti</keyword>
        <type>reg</type>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <text>
            <![CDATA["These controls are in the northern control chamber. Sit in the chair to operate them. It is assumed that you will have full knowledge of their operation."]]>
        </text>
    </node>
    <node for="160">
        <keyword>know</keyword>
        <keyword>oper</keyword>
        <type>reg</type>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <text>
            <![CDATA["Of course. If you don't know how, scrolls of instruction were left behind. If you find one, you will be able to use the controls."]]>
        </text>
    </node>
    <node for="160">
        <keyword>scro</keyword>
        <keyword>inst</keyword>
        <type>reg</type>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <param>0</param>
        <text>
            <![CDATA["Alas, I do not have one."]]>
        </text>
    </node>
